      p.m-about__intro We have what it takes to cater for international clients of all sizes, while we stay true to our roots as little but greatly effective.

    .m-about__text
      p After 5 years of expansion, providing a complete design and marketing communication service from a base across the water, in 2016 we set up in London. So for clients it's the best of both worlds. Because our infrastructure remains mostly in the Czech Republic, which means your budget goes further. Plus you get international talent, Czech reliability (think modern-day Skoda), local British insight, backed up by 20+ years' agency experience from our London associates. We also cover German-speaking markets from Munich, Germany; and the USA from New York. We're members of United Advertising Network, a global pool of agencies sharing the sector's latest innovations, best practice and market research.
      p We partner with the Faculty of Multimedia Communication, the world's 11th best arts and design faculty on the Red Dot global rankings, where we regularly offer work experience to some of the Europe’s brightest and most creative students.

